en-us: Are you age 16+ with at least 2 high-risk medical conditions?
Do you live or work in a long-term care facility?
Examples of this include: skilled nursing facilities, assisted living residences, and rest homes.
All healthcare workers are eligible to receive the vaccine.
Several categories of first responders are eligible for the vaccine in Massachusetts.
Are you a staff member or resident of a congregate care facility?
Examples of congregate care facilities include emergency shelter programs, domestic violence shelters, veterans' shelters, and private special education shools.
All individuals 75+ are eligible for the vaccine.
